{
  "stem": "27351.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, Czestochowa-- Czestochowa's greatest claim to fame is in the cloister of [POLISH], meaning luminous mountain, something like that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a very old cloister, dating I believe from 13th or 14th century.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they have a very famous icon there, the Virgin Mary with the child.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's an interesting icon, because the Virgin Mary is black in this icon.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it's called [POLISH], or black Madonna.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This is-- it's a very rich icon too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's studded with gems.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I had a babysitter, sort of my mother's helper, who would come two, three times a week to help my mother in housework.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Her name was [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hela, ?] Helen, [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Hela. ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Hela ?] was young when I remember her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Hela ?] would sometimes take care of me, go out with me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she would take me to Czestochowa to the cloisters.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I saw the famous icon.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was very, very common for Polish nannies to take Jewish children to churches.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They didn't mean to convert us in any way, just-- I loved [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Hela. ?] She was an interesting person.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She was a very simple girl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she was very attached to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This, of course, did not disturb her, occasionally, to take part in some anti-Semitic little demonstrations, at least our neighbors told us a few times that they saw her together with her friend boyfriend, who was, unfortunately, an alcoholic, and he ruined her.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "However, [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Hela ?] was truly attached to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And after the war, [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Hela ?] found me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I was then in Czestochowa.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And she would drop in into this room that I shared with a few other girls.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She would pick up my dirty clothes, and wash it.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
